{"word":"ἐπιθυμία","slug":"ἐπιθυμία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπιθυμία</b></el> <el>(ἐπιθῡμία, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐπιθυμέω'><el>ἐπιθυμέω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>desire, yearning, longing</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ἐπιθυμίᾳ</el> <i>by passion</i>, <a href='S:opposed to'>opp. to</a> <el>προνοίᾳ</el>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>a longing after</i> a thing, <i>desire of</i> or <i>for</i> it, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; so, <el>ἐπ. πρός τι</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}